column2: eol_SDchla_plot_log <- ggplot(eol_SDchla, aes(x=SD, y=chla)) + geom_point() + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1)) + ggtitle("log-log Plot of Secchi Depth (m) vs Chla (ug/L) in East Okoboji Lake From 2002-2022") + xlab("log Secchi Depth (m)") + ylab("log Chlorophyll a (ug/L)") + scale_x_log10() + scale_y_log10()
